  "title": "Sweet Velvety Lazy Sunday Syrian Cinnamon Stir-fry",
  "description": "A sweet and velvety lazy Sunday Syrian dish featuring ground cinnamon in a hearty stir-fry thats perfect for a casual meal.",
  "cuisine": "Syrian",
